*Tri* godine živela je u Beogradu. (She lived in Belgrade for three years.)

*Tru* se da će se situacija promeniti. (It is said that the situation will change.)

*Trima* je dala pare za kola. (She gave money to three of them for the car.)

*Trom* počinju da se osećaju promene. (They start to feel changes slowly.)

*Trući* je novac za svoje potrebe. (She was spending money for her needs.)